  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TreeNode, JsonSerializable, Iterable<JsonNode>

    public final class JsonArray
extends ArrayNode
    Override of Jackson's ArrayNode

    Unlike in the original, here the list of elements is never null. This allows for much simpler code. Also, the class is final.
